{{MiLB infobox |name = Dominican Summer Orioles |founded = |city = Boca Chica |misc = |logo = Orioles new.PNG |uniformlogo = BaltimoreOriolescap.PNG |class level = Rookie |past class level= |current league = [[Dominican Summer League]] |conference = |division = Boca Chica Baseball City |past league = |majorleague = [[Baltimore Orioles]] |pastmajorleague = |nickname = Orioles |pastnames = |ballpark = Ciudad de Baseball |pastparks = |classchamps = |leaguechamps = |conferencechamps= |divisionchamps = |misc6 = |owner = |manager = Miguel Jabalera |gm = }} The '''Dominican Summer Orioles''' are a [[minor league baseball]] team of the [[Dominican Summer League]]. They are located in [[Boca Chica]], [[Santo Domingo province|Santo Domingo]], [[Dominican Republic]], and play their home games at Ciudad de Baseball. The team plays in the Boca Chica Baseball City division and is affiliated with the [[Baltimore Orioles]].
